# responseBody.Receipt

**Object**

The decoded version of the encoded receipt data that you send with the request to the App Store.

## Declaration

```swift
object responseBody.Receipt
```

## Objects

- **responseBody.Receipt.In_app**: An array that contains the in-app purchase receipt fields for all in-app purchase transactions.

## Objects

- **responseBody.Pending_renewal_info**: An array of elements that refers to open or failed auto-renewable subscription renewals.
- **responseBody.Latest_receipt_info**: An array that contains all in-app purchase transactions.
